title: Low Tertiary Education Completion Rate
description: In 2023, only 46.02% of the population aged 25 and above in Honduras had completed at least a short-cycle tertiary education. This reflects one of the lowest rates globally.

title: Gender Disparity in Tertiary Education
description: As of 2023, there is a slight gender disparity in tertiary education completion in Honduras, with 47.08% of males and 45.15% of females having completed at least a short-cycle tertiary education.
